  <p class="intro">We know that lots of you will be travelling some distance to get to this wedding, and so this page outlines some of the local <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msid=212695573626157084440.0004a840aa7d25b47de8b&amp;msa=0">accommodation options</a>.</p>

